        {
          "reviewTitle": "messy packaging",
          "reviewText": "Neutrogena\u2019s Healthy Skin Sensitive Skin Serum Foundation with Pro-Vitamin B5 is a decent option for those with sensitive skin. The serum-like formula feels light and applies smoothly, which I appreciate for my daily wear. The added Pro-Vitamin B5 does seem to help with hydration, and my skin felt soft after using it. However, I found the coverage to be quite sheer, which might not work for someone looking for more coverage. It also has limited shades, making it challenging to find the perfect match. Overall, it\u2019s a good foundation if you're looking for a lightweight, hydrating base, but it might not meet all coverage or shade needs.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2024",
